#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sale App:</font></b> Manage in-"
"store transactions efficiently, handling sales of seeds, tools, and supplies "
"with ease."
msgstr ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">POS 銷售點管理應用程式</font></b>：高效率地"
"管理實體店交易，輕鬆處理種子、工具等各類用品的銷售工作。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase App:</font></b> Streamline the "
"procurement of farming products from suppliers, managing costs and lead "
"times."
msgstr ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">採購應用程式</font></b>：簡化向供應商採購農"
"產品的流程，控制成本及交貨時間。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Sales App:</font></b> Handle B2B orders "
"and contracts for large farming clients, ensuring accurate pricing."
msgstr ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">銷售應用程式</font></b>：處理大型農場客戶"
"的 B2B 訂單及合約，確保定價準確。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Website App:</font></b><font class=\"text-"
"o-color-3\"> Build a professional online presence to showcase your catalog "
"and attract new customers.</font>"
msgstr ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">網站製作應用程式</font></b>：<font "
"class=\"text-o-color-3\">建立專業的線上形象，展示你的產品目錄，吸引新客戶。</"
"font>"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">eCommerce App:</font></b> Expand your "
"reach by selling products online, offering convenience to modern farmers."
msgstr ""
"<b><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">電子商務應用程式</font></b>：運用網店線上銷"
"售產品，擴大生意範圍，為現代農民提供方便快捷的購物方式。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Accounting:</b> Automatically log payments, close sessions, and generate "
"tax reports."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Automatic Delivery:</b> Once the quote is\n"
"                    accepted, it's possible to deliver the products just\n"
"                    as it does for a regular e-commerce order."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Capture Requests:</b> Any submission via the <b>\"Contact\n"
"                    Us\"</b> page instantly generates a new <b>CRM "
"opportunity</b>."
msgstr ""
"<b>捕捉客戶需求</b>：透過「<b>聯絡我們</b>」\n"
"                    頁面提交的任何請求，都會即時產生一項新的 <b>CRM 銷售商機"
"</b>。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Crucial Review:</b> You must review all e-commerce settings to ensure "
"they align with your internal business policies (e.g., when invoices are "
"generated, whether a mandatory customer check-in is required for ordering, "
"etc.)."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Define B2B Pricing:</b> Create and assign a <b>dedicated\n"
"                    pricelist</b> to each B2B contact. Ensure this pricelist "
"is active on your\n"
"                    website so the customer sees their agreed-upon prices "
"upon login."
msgstr ""
"<b>制定 B2B 價目表</b>：你可為每位 B2B 聯絡人建立及指定<b>專屬價目表</b>。\n"
"                    記得將相關價目表設定為在網站上可用，\n"
"                    讓客戶登入後即可看見雙方協定的價格。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Delivery Methods:</b> Go to <b>Website &gt; Configuration &gt; Delivery "
"Methods</b> \n"
"                    to define all available options and their costs."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>E-commerce Category:</b> For easier product retrieval by customers on "
"your online store."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>External Providers:</b> Check if a predefined Odoo connection exists if "
"you \n"
"                            work with specific shipping carriers."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Field Service:</b> Implement this module if you <b>offer on-site repair "
"or maintenance services</b>."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>In-Store Pickup (Click &amp; Collect):</b> If you wish to offer this, "
"you \n"
"                            must <b>activate the setting</b> within the "
"<b>Website Settings</b> first."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Key Product Settings:</b>"
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Layout Settings:</b> Adjust the visual presentation and layout of "
"products using the <b>website editor</b>."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Loyalty Programs:</b> Implement <b>loyalty cards</b> as a core\n"
"                            strategy to <b>activate customer retention</b> "
"and increase lifetime\n"
"                            value."
msgstr ""
"<b>會員/忠誠度計劃</b>：推行<b>會員卡</b>作為核心\n"
"                            策略，以<b>提升客戶留存率</b>，增加客戶的終身\n"
"                            價值。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Note:</b> Increased capability leads to higher complexity and more "
"maintenance."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Our Advice:</b> Stick with your current streamlined configuration until "
"you’re fully comfortable. When you're ready to upgrade, try the Inventory "
"module on a duplicated database first to ensure it fits your workflow. 😉"
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Payment Providers &amp; Methods:</b> Go to <b>Website\n"
"                    &gt; Configuration &gt; Payment Providers</b> and "
"install <b>all</b> the payment\n"
"                    methods and providers you plan to offer (e.g., credit "
"card processors, PayPal,\n"
"                    etc.)."
msgstr ""
"<b>付款服務商及付款方式</b>：前往<b>網站 \n"
"                    &gt; 配置 &gt; 付款服務商</b>，安裝<b>所有</b>你打算提供"
"的\n"
"                    付款方式及付款服務商，例如：信用卡處理商、PayPal \n"
"                    等。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Payroll:</b> Use this feature to handle <b>employee salaries and manage "
"holiday requests</b>."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Point of Sale Category:</b> For organizing transactions within your shop "
"system."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Pricelist Segmentation:</b> Define multiple pricing structures for the\n"
"                            same product, supporting different business "
"models (e.g., B2B vs. B2C)\n"
"                            and enabling <b>client-specific pricing "
"contracts</b>."
msgstr ""
"<b>價目表細分</b>：你可為同一項產品設定多種定價結構，\n"
"                            支援各類業務模式（例如：B2B 企業對企業、B2C 企業"
"對消費者等），\n"
"                            同時支援<b>為指定客戶制定特別價格合約</b>。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Product Category:</b> For internal tracking and reporting."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Product-Level Settings:</b> Define core product settings directly on the "
"<b>product form</b>."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Promotional Agility:</b> Use <b>discounts and promotions</b> to\n"
"                            quickly adjust pricing for sales events or to "
"give targeted, <b>manual\n"
"                            reductions</b> at the point of sale."
msgstr ""
"<b>優惠靈活度</b>：利用<b>折扣及促銷優惠</b>，\n"
"                            快速調整促銷活動的優惠價格，或在銷售點\n"
"                            <b>手動打折</b>、提供有針對性的折扣。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Publishing:</b> Each product can be <b>publishe independently</b> on your "
"online store."
msgstr ""

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Qualify Leads:</b> Engage with the client through\n"
"                    the CRM opportunity to fully understand their request—"
"whether it's a need for a\n"
"                    specific product, a supplier inquiry, or general "
"information."
msgstr ""
"<b>評定潛在客戶資格</b>：利用 CRM 客戶關係管理系統，\n"
"                    與客戶保持互動，充份理解他們的需求，\n"
"                    無論是想尋找指定產品，供應商諮詢，還是一般查詢，都妥善管"
"理。"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Quote and Confirm:</b> If a specific demand\n"
"                    requires pricing, generate a <b>quotation directly from "
"the opportunity</b>. The\n"
"                    client can then <b>confirm and sign it online</b>."
msgstr ""
"<b>報價及確認</b>：若某項需求\n"
"                    需要特別定價，<b>可在銷售商機畫面中，直接產生報價單</"
"b>。\n"
"                    客戶隨後可<b>透過線上方式，確認並簽署報價單</b>。"

