msgid ""
"Fast Root Fertilizer is a potent and specialized formula designed to promote "
"rapid root development in plants. Packed with essential nutrients and growth "
"stimulants, this fertilizer accelerates the establishment of strong and "
"healthy root systems, enhancing overall plant growth and vitality."
msgstr ""
"Fast Root 肥料運用有效的專門配方，為促進植物根部快速發育而設計。這種肥料富含"
"必需營養素及刺激生長物質，可加速植物建立強健和健康的根系，增強植物的整體活"
"力，激發成長。"

