#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model:product.template,description_sale:agriculture_shop.product_product_17_product_template
msgid ""
"Safaya Pesticide is a trusted solution designed to protect crops from "
"harmful pests and ensure their healthy growth. With its advanced formula, "
"Safaya effectively targets a wide range of pests while minimizing "
"environmental impact. By safeguarding plants from infestations, this "
"pesticide contributes to higher yields and quality harvests, promoting "
"sustainable agricultural practices."
msgstr ""
"Safaya 殺蟲劑是獲信賴的解決方案，旨在保護農作物免受害蟲侵害，確保它們健康生"
"長。憑藉其先進配方，Safaya 能有效消滅多種害蟲，同時將環境影響減至最低。此殺蟲"
"劑透過保護植物免受侵襲，有助提高產量及收成質素，促進可持續的農耕做法。"

